```typescript
const headers = {
  'X-API-Key': API_KEY,  // From environment
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json',
};
```

### Proxy vs Direct URL
```typescript
// For API calls (via proxy)
const API_BASE = '/api/rest';

// For applookup values (direct)
